    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经营属于自己的动物训导中心!</h2>动物训导师模拟器将赋予你一个绝无仅有的机会来建造、设计和经营属于自己的训导中心! 打造一个完美的空间，让在这里接受训练的动物们感到安全和愉悦。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/1e573a7dc417c032aab3e8d1ee0cbcc2.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/1e573a7dc417c032aab3e8d1ee0cbcc2.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/1e573a7dc417c032aab3e8d1ee0cbcc2.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不断对训导中心发展提升</h2>以极为新颖的布置和训练设施展现不断提升的训练中心 - 斜坡跳跃、障碍赛、回旋标杆、隧道等等。管理好整个区域，不断对其进行扩充，建造一个大厅，放些椅子，刷一下墙，分隔出等候室，再给动物们布置出一个游乐区。千万记得，在你的动物训导中心里，将会有多种动物共存 - 因此，你需要考虑好，它们各自不同的生活空间。无论如何，每种动物都有自己独有的需求。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/032f3c915ba2fa80013ca4ecaf70cd1d.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/032f3c915ba2fa80013ca4ecaf70cd1d.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/032f3c915ba2fa80013ca4ecaf70cd1d.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >细心地照料它们</h2>锻炼和训练活动不代表生活的全部 - 在游戏中你的任务也包括对这些动物无微不至的照料。爱抚、刷、洗它们，还有别忘了按时喂它们! 由此，每只动物在你的训导中心生活都会有家的感觉。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/a334b5e2a796fa26126d4166a766d19d.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/a334b5e2a796fa26126d4166a766d19d.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/a334b5e2a796fa26126d4166a766d19d.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恰当的训练能提升动物们的技能</h2>在游戏中你的主要任务之一就是训导动物，教会它们如何听取命令以及行动技巧。这在很大程度上将取决于你和你训导动物的方法如何，这需要大量的苦练和投入，但动物们将会用对你的爱及忠诚来回报你的付出。对于有些动物来说，并不要急于进行训练和适应新的习惯，应该先找到正确与之相处的方法才好。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/03ebc80e5f4a62d060cec007eb70685b.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/03ebc80e5f4a62d060cec007eb70685b.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/03ebc80e5f4a62d060cec007eb70685b.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多参加各种竞赛</h2>建设一个种马场和一个围场，加以训练，或许其中会有某匹马能在世锦赛中夺冠也说不定! 艰苦的训练绝对是有回报的，努力把你的训导中心发展成世界上最棒的、最知名的一所吧!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/9c6f7307ef6f9d75192f41edecd9841a.poster.avif?t=1761218319\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/9c6f7307ef6f9d75192f41edecd9841a.webm?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199860/extras/9c6f7307ef6f9d75192f41edecd9841a.mp4?t=1761218319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
